(22, 22, 'Custom Software Development', 'Custom software development services that turn your ideas into scalable, secure, and high-performing digital solutions.', '<p>Turn your vision into a powerful digital reality with our advanced software development services. At the heart of our approach lies a commitment to delivering tailor-made software solutions that are precisely aligned with your business goals. From innovative web applications and high-performing mobile apps to robust enterprise software systems, we design and build solutions that drive growth, efficiency, and customer satisfaction. Our team of experienced developers, designers, and strategists work closely with you at every stage— from concept and architecture to deployment and ongoing support—ensuring the final product not only meets but exceeds your expectations. With a focus on scalability, security, and user experience, we transform your ideas into smart, functional, and future-ready software solutions.</p>', NULL, 'en', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-07-23 20:28:01', '2025-07-24 13:54:18', 'Custom Solutions', 'Tailor-made software aligned precisely with your unique business needs and goals.', 'Full Lifecycle Support', 'From concept to maintenance, we manage every stage of the development process.', 'Scalable & Secure', 'Solutions built for growth with strong security and future-ready architecture.', 'User-Centric Design', 'Designed with intuitive interfaces to enhance user experience and satisfaction.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(23, 23, 'Cybersecurity', 'Comprehensive cybersecurity solutions for threat detection, prevention, compliance, and risk management to safeguard your business.', '<p>Safeguard your digital environment with our comprehensive and state-of-the-art cybersecurity solutions. In today’s ever-evolving threat landscape, protecting your data and systems is more critical than ever. Our team of cybersecurity specialists provides end-to-end protection, covering everything from real-time threat detection, prevention, and incident response to compliance management and strategic risk mitigation. We work closely with you to identify vulnerabilities, implement robust defense mechanisms, and ensure your business remains secure, compliant, and resilient. Whether you\'re facing external threats, internal risks, or industry-specific security challenges, our tailored solutions are designed to give you peace of mind and keep your operations running smoothly. Let us help you stay one step ahead of cybercriminals with proactive, intelligent, and reliable cybersecurity.</p>', NULL, 'en', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-07-23 20:41:32', '2025-07-24 14:00:12', 'End-to-End Protection', 'Comprehensive security from threat detection to incident response and compliance.', 'Proactive Defense', 'Stay ahead of cyber threats with real-time monitoring and intelligent prevention.', 'Risk & Compliance', 'Ensure regulatory compliance while minimizing security risks across your operations.', 'Tailored Solutions', 'Customized cybersecurity strategies built around your industry and business needs.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(24, 24, 'Cloud Computing', 'Scalable, flexible, and efficient cloud solutions—tailored to your needs for seamless migration, management, and growth.', '<div>Unlock the full potential of your business with our cutting-edge cloud solutions, designed to bring scalability, flexibility, and efficiency to your operations. As organizations increasingly turn to the cloud for agility and innovation, we offer end-to-end services that help you seamlessly migrate, manage, and optimize your cloud infrastructure. Whether you require a public, private, or hybrid cloud environment, our team works closely with you to understand your specific needs and craft customized solutions that align with your goals. From reducing operational costs and simplifying IT management to enabling remote collaboration and boosting productivity, our cloud services empower you to stay competitive in a fast-paced digital landscape. Experience the freedom and performance of a future-ready cloud ecosystem, tailored to scale as your business evolves.</div>', NULL, 'en', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-07-23 20:46:00', '2025-07-24 13:59:01', 'Scalable Infrastructure', 'Cloud solutions that grow with your business and adapt to changing demands.', 'Seamless Migration', 'Smooth transition to the cloud with minimal disruption and maximum efficiency.', 'Tailored Environments', 'Customized public, private, or hybrid cloud setups to fit your exact needs.', 'Enhanced Productivity', 'Boost collaboration, reduce costs, and streamline IT operations with smart cloud management.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(25, 25, 'Data Analytics and AI', 'Leverage data analytics and AI to uncover insights, predict trends, and drive smarter business decisions.', '<p>Transform raw data into powerful insights with our advanced data analytics and AI services. In an era where data drives competitive advantage, we help you harness its full potential to make smarter, faster, and more strategic decisions. Our solutions are designed to uncover hidden patterns, forecast trends, and deliver actionable intelligence that empowers every level of your organization. Whether you’re looking to optimize operations, enhance customer experiences, or explore new growth opportunities, our team leverages cutting-edge tools and machine learning models to turn complex data into clear, meaningful outcomes. From data visualization and predictive analytics to AI-driven automation, we provide the technology and expertise you need to stay ahead in a data-driven world.</p>', NULL, 'en', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-07-23 20:49:07', '2025-07-24 13:57:47', 'Actionable Insights', 'Turn complex data into clear, strategic, and impactful business intelligence.', 'Predictive Analytics', 'Forecast trends and make informed decisions with advanced data modeling.', 'AI-Powered Solutions', 'Leverage machine learning for smarter automation and deeper analysis.', 'End-to-End Expertise', 'From visualization to implementation, we support your full data journey.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(26, 26, 'Full-Cycle Services', 'End-to-end software development services—from concept to maintenance—ensuring reliable, scalable solutions tailored to your goals.', '<p>From initial concept to final deployment and ongoing maintenance, we manage the entire development lifecycle with precision and care. Our end-to-end approach ensures that every technical detail is expertly handled, allowing you to concentrate on what matters most—growing your core business. Whether it\'s planning, designing, building, testing, or supporting your solution, our team is with you every step of the way. We simplify the complex, eliminate guesswork, and deliver reliable, scalable solutions that align perfectly with your goals. Let us handle the technology, so you can stay focused on driving success.</p>', NULL, 'en', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-07-23 20:50:45', '2025-07-24 13:55:53', 'End-to-End Service', 'We manage the complete development lifecycle from planning to ongoing support.', 'Business-Focused', 'You focus on growth while we handle all the technical complexities.', 'Scalable Solutions', 'Built to adapt and grow alongside your evolving business needs.', 'Expert Guidance', 'Our team supports you at every stage with precision and care.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);

